      <title>Windhorst 旗下 La Perla 停止向员工支付工资，英国诉讼搁置</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/lars-windhorst-s-la-perla-stopped-paying-employees-uk-suit-says</link>
